subject: Reminder — Your Rental Starts in 2 Hours
<h2>Rental Reminder</h2>
<p>Hi {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your bike rental at <strong>{{ hub_name }}</strong> starts in 2 hours.</p>
<table>
  <tr><td><strong>Booking ID:</strong></td><td>{{ booking_id }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Bike Model:</strong></td><td>{{ model_name }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Start Time:</strong></td><td>{{ start_date }} {{ start_time }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Hub Address:</strong></td><td>{{ hub_address }}</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Please bring your ID documents for verification. Late arrivals may result in your booking being released.</p>
